|------|---------|---------|
| `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/delhi/app/src/client/components/graph/DescriptionSection.tsx` | 4-7, 18, 72, 74 | Frontend `SourceRef` type and `.tb` access |
| `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/delhi/app/src/server/extraction/types.ts` | 12-14 | Backend `TbRecordId` and typed record exports |
